  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You launch yourself into the air using all your might and then crash down in a mighty slam, shattering the world beneath you.</p><p>You jump up to ten times your Strength score into the air and fall to earth, forcing creatures in an area equal to double your Strength score to make a Dexterity saving throw. On a failed save, they take your unarmed damage + the falling damage you would have taken as bludgeoning damage and are knocked prone.</p><p>On a successful save, they take half as much damage and are still knocked prone. You leave a crater a number of feet deep equal to your Strength score. An area of difficult terrain is left in your wake with a radius three times your Strength score.</p>",
